{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":599323,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我上一次也是唯一一次写完一篇小说是在小学四年级 现在那个带着校徽的作业本还在我家书柜上🚬","timestamp":1606047317,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599334,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"看过一些指导写作的文章 让我印象最深刻的就是不要停下来 不要因为怕写得不好而停下来思考 写就完事儿了。\n如果要求很高的话 也有一句话叫好文章都是改出来的\n纯纯业余 跑了quq","timestamp":1606047453,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599341,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"嗯嗯嗯，算是自娱自乐，然后就很有想要表达的东西，强迫自己开了个头，然后就停不下来了","timestamp":1606047491,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599343,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"写作助理，预约yh，yyds","timestamp":1606047509,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599345,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"初中写过，写得不好，其实真的有想法有热情一动笔都停不下来的","timestamp":1606047551,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599353,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"cz写过临高启明的同人hhhh","timestamp":1606047659,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599361,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"蹲👀","timestamp":1606047769,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599373,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"用爱发电","timestamp":1606047906,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":599377,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":124463,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"alice